      <p>Complementary to your clinical regenerative treatment, we suggest using our physician-designed&nbsp;<a href="https://qcjointhealth.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Joint &amp; Bone supplement</a>, created to reduce inflammation and improve joint health.</p>

